metadata.description:
A collection of over twenty Norwegian folk tales and fairy tales including: Reynard and the Cock, The Giant Who Had No Heart in his Body, and Why the Sea is Salt.


You can also read a copy of 'East O'The Sun And West O'The Moon: With Other Norwegian Folk Tales' by going to the International Children's Digital Library, a joint project of the Internet Archive and University Of Maryland.
metadata.title: East O'The Sun And West O'The Moon: With Other Norwegian Folk Tales
